article.description: — Joe Quintana scored 16 points and Hunter Goodrick scored 14 off the bench on 7-for-11 shooting and California Baptist beat NJIT 59-43 on Friday night.
article.headline: Quintana, Goodrick help carry Cal Baptist past NJIT
article.linkText: Quintana, Goodrick help carry Cal Baptist past NJIT
article.story: RIVERSIDE, Calif. -- — Joe Quintana scored 16 points and Hunter Goodrick scored 14 off the bench on 7-for-11 shooting and California Baptist beat NJIT 59-43 on Friday night. Taran Armstrong added 11 points for the Lancers (1-1). Souleyman Diakite scored 12 points shooting 5 for 5 and making both foul shots. Mekhi Gray scored 11 off the bench for the Highlanders (0-2). Diakite made his free throws with 13:25 remaining and Cal Baptist proceeded to outscore NJIT 13-0 over the next six minutes to seal it. ------
